{% comment %}
  Research layout — standalone document reproducing /mockups/research.html.
  Publication entries are hardcoded exactly as in the mockup (driving them from
  _bibliography/papers.bib via jekyll-scholar is a follow-up, see
  IMPLEMENTATION_NOTES.md). Only the three working-paper "wp" pills that carry
  real arXiv URLs in the mockup are live; every other pill is href="#".
  Section ids must match the mockup verbatim for the scroll-spy in head.liquid.
{% endcomment %}
